creator: Tickeron, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Easy for beginner traders and comprehensive for crypto experts, Tickeron has the best tools for quick crypto search, analysis, and trading ideas.

Tickeron makes it easy to search and find great cryptocurrencies to buy and sell. Follow your favorite crypto, and learn to understand the market.

Create a personalized watchlist to track charts, crypto quotes, and daily/weekly/monthly/yearly performance.

Buy and Sell recommendations are updated 24/7.
Know which cryptos to Buy and Sell: at the right time and price!

The Tickeron app is perfect for Day Traders, Swing Traders, and Long Term Crypto Investors -- our timely, accurate, and verifiable recommendations and alerts work to boost your trading!

Crypto Ratings
Create crypto watchlists with personalized live crypto market signals and buy and sell recommendations.
View rating history across days, weeks, and months in the past to validate the accuracy of app predictions.
Filter your watchlists to only see cryptos with particular ratings to save time and maximize your trading profits.

Crypto Market News and Real-Time Quotes
Our technical analysis signals are based on Moving Averages, RSI, Stochastics, MACD, Bollinger Bands, and more.

Crypto Watchlists and Signals
Create watchlists to track cryptocurrencies in real-time.
Tickeron's Crypto Signals (Alerts) gives you customizable alerts for cryptos. You can set up notifications for a specific price, change by %, or volume.
Alerts help you track market changes and act instantaneously to invest or sell profitably.

Select your crypto trading strategy with Tickeron's AI Robots -- backed by 100+ of backtested algorithms. No trading experience needed!
With AI Robots you can view live buy and sell trades with potential profit and stop loss.
Receive timely alerts with each trade. The backtested AI models are updated in real-time, giving crypto investors daily recommendations that can outperform the market by 50-90%
